      • getUniqueVehicleId

        public java.lang.String getUniqueVehicleId()
        Use this method to guarantee the 2020 is connected to the same vehicle. Temporarily just returns the Device ID, but will eventually return a hash code based on the VIN and the GPSSN.
        Returns:
        A string uniquely identifying the vehicle this device is connected to. Typically will be a combination of VIN and GPSSN.
